{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1081,"text":"According to the UN,"},{"time":3111,"text":"billions of people still live\nwithout an address."},{"time":7154,"text":"The economist Hernando de Soto said,"},{"time":9459,"text":"\"Without an address,"},{"time":10841,"text":"you live outside the law."},{"time":12767,"text":"You might as well not exist.\""},{"time":15679,"text":"I'm here to tell you how my team and I\nare trying to change that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19986,"text":"If you go to an online map\nand look at a favela in Brazil"},{"time":23226,"text":"or a township in South Africa,"},{"time":25074,"text":"you'll see a few streets\nbut a lot of empty space."},{"time":28678,"text":"But if you flip to satellite view,"},{"time":30845,"text":"there are thousands of people,\nhomes and businesses"},{"time":33983,"text":"in this vast, unmapped\nand unaddressed spaces."},{"time":37551,"text":"In Ghana's capital, Accra,"},{"time":39435,"text":"there are numbers and letters\nscrawled onto the sides of walls,"},{"time":43548,"text":"where they piloted address systems\nbut not finished them."},{"time":48163,"text":"But these places,\nthese unaddressed places,"},{"time":51323,"text":"hold huge economic potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55201,"text":"Here's why the issue\nof addressing stuck with me."},{"time":58453,"text":"I worked in the music\nbusiness for 10 years,"},{"time":60529,"text":"and what you may not know\nabout the music world"},{"time":62931,"text":"is that every day, people struggle\nwith the problems of addressing."},{"time":66368,"text":"So from the musicians\nwho have to find the gigs"},{"time":69221,"text":"to the production companies\nwho bring the equipment,"},{"time":71674,"text":"everyone somehow always gets lost."},{"time":73760,"text":"We even had to add someone\nto our schedules"},{"time":75925,"text":"who was the person you called\nwhen you thought you'd arrived"},{"time":78768,"text":"but then realized you hadn't."},{"time":80176,"text":"And we had some pretty bad days,"},{"time":82523,"text":"like in Italy, where a truck driver\nunloaded all the equipment"},{"time":85732,"text":"an hour north of Rome,\nnot an hour south of Rome,"},{"time":88339,"text":"and a slightly worse day"},{"time":89572,"text":"where a keyboard player\ncalled me and said,"},{"time":91671,"text":"\"Chris, don't panic,\nbut we may have just sound-checked"},{"time":94609,"text":"at the wrong people's wedding.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":96196,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":97795,"text":"So not long after the fated Rome event,"},{"time":100457,"text":"I chatted this through\nwith a friend of mine"},{"time":102590,"text":"who is a mathematician,"},{"time":103778,"text":"and we thought it was a problem\nwe could do something about."},{"time":106612,"text":"We thought, well,\nwe could make a new system,"},{"time":108973,"text":"but it shouldn't look like the old system."},{"time":111628,"text":"We agreed that addresses were bad."},{"time":114474,"text":"We knew we wanted something very precise,"},{"time":116524,"text":"but GPS coordinates,\nlatitude and longitude,"},{"time":118903,"text":"were just too complicated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121256,"text":"So we divided the world\ninto three-meter squares."},{"time":124583,"text":"The world divides into around 57 trillion\nthree-meter squares,"},{"time":128700,"text":"and we found that there are\nenough combinations"},{"time":130915,"text":"of three dictionary words"},{"time":132749,"text":"that we could name every three-meter\nsquare in the world uniquely"},{"time":136365,"text":"with just three words."},{"time":138546,"text":"We used 40,000 words,"},{"time":140141,"text":"so that's 40,000 cubed,"},{"time":141758,"text":"64 trillion combinations of three words,"},{"time":145015,"text":"which is more than enough for\nthe 57-trillion-odd three-meter squares,"},{"time":148927,"text":"with a few spare."},{"time":151044,"text":"So that's exactly what we did."},{"time":153017,"text":"We divided the world\ninto three-meter squares,"},{"time":156115,"text":"gave each one a unique,\nthree-word identifier --"},{"time":158980,"text":"what we call a three-word address."},{"time":161385,"text":"So for example, right here,"},{"time":164481,"text":"I'm standing at mustards.coupons.pinup,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166858,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168032,"text":"but over here ..."},{"time":170753,"text":"I'm standing at pinched.\nsingularly.tutorial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177133,"text":"But we haven't just done this in English."},{"time":179128,"text":"We thought it was essential that people\nshould be able to use this system"},{"time":182581,"text":"in their own language."},{"time":183867,"text":"So far, we've built it into 14 languages,"},{"time":186124,"text":"including French, Swahili and Arabic,"},{"time":188591,"text":"and we're working on more now,\nlike Xhosa, Zulu and Hindi."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193157,"text":"But this idea can do a lot more"},{"time":195028,"text":"than just get my musicians\nto their gigs on time."},{"time":197752,"text":"If the 75 percent of countries\nthat struggle with reliable addressing"},{"time":201953,"text":"started using three-word addresses,"},{"time":203681,"text":"there's a stack of far more\nimportant applications."},{"time":208033,"text":"In Durban, South Africa,"},{"time":210487,"text":"an NGO called Gateway Health"},{"time":212168,"text":"have distributed 11,000\nthree-word address signs"},{"time":215142,"text":"to their community,"},{"time":216555,"text":"so the pregnant mothers,\nwhen they go into labor,"},{"time":218958,"text":"can call the emergency services"},{"time":220790,"text":"and tell them exactly\nwhere to pick them up from,"},{"time":223165,"text":"because otherwise, the ambulances\nhave often taken hours to find them."},{"time":226964,"text":"In Mongolia, the National Post Service\nhave adopted the system"},{"time":230265,"text":"and are now doing deliveries\nto many people's houses"},{"time":232727,"text":"for the first time."},{"time":234152,"text":"The UN are using it\nto geotag photos in disaster zones"},{"time":237859,"text":"so they can deliver aid\nto exactly the right place."},{"time":240555,"text":"Even Domino's Pizza\nare using it in the Caribbean,"},{"time":243249,"text":"because they haven't been able\nto find customers' homes,"},{"time":245974,"text":"but they really want to get\ntheir pizza to them while its still hot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249729,"text":"Shortly, you'll be able to get into a car,"},{"time":252274,"text":"speak the three words,"},{"time":254034,"text":"and the car will navigate you\nto that exact spot."},{"time":257888,"text":"In Africa, the continent\nhas leapfrogged phone lines"},{"time":261437,"text":"to go to mobile phones,"},{"time":262854,"text":"bypassed traditional banks\nto go straight to mobile payments."},{"time":267298,"text":"We're really proud that the post services\nof three African countries --"},{"time":271276,"text":"Nigeria, Djibouti and CÃ´te d'Ivoire,"},{"time":273896,"text":"have gone straight to adopting\nthree-word addresses,"},{"time":276572,"text":"which means that people in those countries"},{"time":278669,"text":"have a really simple way\nto explain where they live, today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283167,"text":"For me, poor addressing\nwas an annoying frustration,"},{"time":286870,"text":"but for billions of people,"},{"time":289398,"text":"it's a huge business inefficiency,"},{"time":291835,"text":"severely hampers\ntheir infrastructure growth,"},{"time":294540,"text":"and can cost lives."},{"time":296837,"text":"We're on a mission to change that,"},{"time":298489,"text":"three words at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299726,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300901,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}